citances.sentence: 2 This appeal proceeded pursuant to leave to appeal which I granted on 16 October 2008 ( Tervonen v Finland [2008] FCA 1539) ('the leave judgment'). In the leave judgment I concluded, applying the conventional test in Décor Corporation Pty Ltd v Dart Industries Inc [1991] FCA 655 ; (1991) 33 FCR 397 , that Mr Tervonen was entitled to consideration by a Full Court of his arguments that Flick J had erred in dismissing his application under s 39B of the Judiciary Act 1903 (Cth), which sought to attack a request made by Finland on 27 July 2006 for his extradition.
